  //   main_k1..k30  — 30-key alpha core, inner 5 cols per hand
  //                   × 3 rows (top / home / bottom)
  //   main_k31..k40 — number row (10 slots, one per alpha col)
  //   main_k41..k50 — outer columns; halcyon fills the pinky-outer
  //                   column on each hand across all 4 rows
  //
  // Geometric y carries the col-stag splay:
  //   pinky-outer & pinky-inner: pulled back 0.75
  //   ring:    pulled back 0.25
  //   middle:  pushed forward 0.5
  //   index-outer: pulled back 0.25
  //   index-inner: baseline
